    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood trees belonging to the genus Pyrus, pale pinkish-brown in color with a very fine texture. It is used for making bowls, brush handles, drawing instruments, and cabinetry.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
